# Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline Project using Docker on AWS EC2

This project demonstrates a complete CI/CD pipeline implementation using Jenkins, Docker, GitHub, and AWS EC2.

The pipeline automates:
- Pulling source code from GitHub
- Building a Docker image
- Running the application container automatically

---

